    "We then design a controlled study where we isolate the impact of new knowledge and rigorously evaluate its effects.",
    "We provide multiple insights on the fine-tuning dynamics, with the following key findings: (1) Acquiring new knowledge via supervised fine-tuning is correlated with hallucinations w.r.t.",
    "pre-existing knowledge.",
    "(2) LLMs struggle to integrate new knowledge through fine-tuning and mostly learn to use their pre-existing knowledge.",
    "Our experiments were conducted using a single LLM, and thus it is unclear whether results will vary with different LLMs."
